Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content: ZecMiner64.exe -zpool stratum+tcp://pool.piratechain.org:3031 -zwal zcwalletaddressherefromagama -zpsw x

Content: I think these portions are needed but I've never used Claymore so someone who has will have to chime in...

Content:
setx GPU_FORCE_64BIT_PTR 0
setx GPU_MAX_HEAP_SIZE 100
setx GPU_USE_SYNC_OBJECTS 1
setx GPU_MAX_ALLOC_PERCENT 100
setx GPU_SINGLE_ALLOC_PERCENT 100

Author: FishyGuts#5085
Content: ZecMiner64.exe -zpool stratum+tcp://pool.piratechain.org:3031 -zwal zcwalletaddressherefromagama -zpsw x
